情况”“用手机就能遥控操作”“摆脱遥控器，完全通过语音来控制电视”，这些便是老年用户对智能电视功能的需求。"},"attached_info":"Cj4I34vf4OTo94QBEAMaCDc2MTY3MTU5IJXgo48GMAQ4PUAWcgk1MTI0ODU1MjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"66 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-81869c526c54ecac1955980559442fbe_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1642939982.0700011","card_id":"Q_34452810","target":{"id":34452810,"title":"冬天跑步应该穿什么衣服？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/34452810","type":"question","created":1439272751,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":619,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[844,4797,40811,44607,106007],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"秋天来了，冬天不远了。 我今年刚开始跑步。 夏天都是短衫短裤的跑。 但是天气冷的时候不知道应该穿什么跑。 我汗腺十分发达，穿个大衣跑也不是个事啊。 微冷 一般冷 超级冷 分别怎么穿？"},"attached_info":"Cj0I34vf4OTo94QBEAMaBzU5ODc0OTIgr56mrgUwADjrBEAXcggzNDQ1MjgxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f991ed2af87daf732d8aaaefa79d11b1_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1642939982.0704582","card_id":"Q_20539701","target":{"id":20539701,"title":"怎样背书才能背得最快？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/20539701","type":"question","created":1350540504,"answer_count":382,"follower_count":18674,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3798,4570,5361,27839,124085],"comment_count":9,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0I34vf4OTo94QBEAMaBjM5NjM0OSDYuf6DBTAJOPKRAUAYcggyMDUzOTcwMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4aa2cde714438dcf537f9e6035fe7032_b.jpg"}]},